,'es','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1434','Bulldog'),(9635,'es','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1435','Caniche'),(9636,'es','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1436','Fox terrier'),(9637,'it','App\\Entity\\Question','content','359','Quale cane un tempo era adatto alla caccia alle anatre in acqua ?'),(9638,'it','App\\Entity\\Question','explanation','359','Questo tipo di caccia spiega la toelettatura del leone che spesso vi viene praticata e che era molto di moda durante la Belle Époque.'),(9639,'it','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1433','Barboncino'),(9640,'it','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1435','Fox Terrier'),(9641,'it','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1436','Pechinese'),(9642,'nl','App\\Entity\\Question','content','359','Welke hond was ooit geschikt voor de eendenjacht in het water ?'),(9643,'nl','App\\Entity\\Question','explanation','359','Deze vorm van jacht verklaart de leeuwenverzorging die er vaak op wordt toegepast en die tijdens de Belle Époque erg in de mode was.'),(9644,'nl','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1433','Buldog'),(9645,'nl','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1434','Pekinees'),(9646,'nl','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1435','Foxterriër'),(9647,'nl','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1436','Poedel'),(9648,'fr','App\\Entity\\Question','content','360','Quelle race belge de petite taille est caractérisée par son museau écrasé ?'),(9649,'fr','App\\Entity\\Question','explanation','360','La race est issue de croisements effectués au XIXe siècle entre le smousje (chien à poil dur), l\'épagneul King Charles et le carlin.'),(9650,'fr','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1437','Teckel'),(9651,'fr','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1438','Basset'),(9652,'fr','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1439','Malinois'),(9653,'fr','App\\Entity\\Proposal','content','1440','Griffon belge'),(9654,'en','App\\Entity\\Question','content','360','Which small Belgian breed is characterized by its crushed muzzle ?'),(9655,'en','App\\Entity\\Question','exp